                        deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
                    </p>
                    <div class="project__small-images">
                        <img
                            src={imgPmOne}
                            alt="Icon of a Conversation Bubble"
                        />
                        <img
                            src={imgPmTwo}
                            alt="Icon of a Conversation Bubble"
